cause.description:
WOSU Public Radio offers the citizens of Central Ohio and worldwide high quality news and information and classical music.  WOSU is recognized as an indispensable multimedia and technology resource connecting community through preeminent programming and services. The organization and its employees will be leaders in building innovative models of community service that engage people in ideas, issues, and the diverse cultural life of our region.

You can also join the WOSU Facebook group at http://tinyurl.com/269anq.




1. Serve our community through programming excellence that provides knowledge and new ideas for personal enrichment and to encourage active and meaningful citizenship; 

2. Recognize, embrace, and express the high value we place on diversity inour programming and our workplace; 

3. Provide creative application of technology to consistently meet the changing needs and interests of our community;
